備註 Remarks
     1. Every even week's language lab classroom: Hsiu-chi Building 26103.
2. Students are strongly recommended to ask event leave ahead of class and sick leave right after that class they are absent. All students are allowed to be absent ONLY for the very first 2 hours; after these very first 2 hours, all absent hours will be counted and recorded. Over-absenteeism will be reported to school and those who are of over-absenteeism are not allowed to attend the final exam according to the school's student regulations.
3. The General Proficiency Exam: (30%); Self-study: (5%)
4. Oral test may be frequently held in lab classroom in Hsiu-chi Building.




