 Language Proficiency and Communication Abilities
 

課程概述 Course Description
       訓練使用一般英文學術性字彙，以增進學生英文口語表達及批判思考能力。 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
Improve students’ English proficiency with adequate opportunities of practice.Topics cover global themes of arts, social concerns, and technology.The oral training helps students develop daily communicative skills daily. Build students' confidence and techniques needed in academic presentations.Familiarize students with grammar, vocabulary, and the mechanics of English.Encourage students to be a better speaker by saying what they really think.Encourage students to listen a lot and learn conversational phrases. Encourage students to keep expanding their vocabulary and take the initiative.Encourage students not to be afraid to ask and make mistakes IN ENGLISH. 

